<subSubSection id="11D265234549B64BB595FEFBFF791F44" pageId="10" pageNumber="469" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="597736A84549B64BB595FEFBFF791F44" blockId="10.[151,1437,150,572]" pageId="10" pageNumber="469">
<emphasis id="6BBCEABA4549B64BB595FEFBFE801CF0" bold="true" box="[199,317,366,392]" pageId="10" pageNumber="469">Remarks:</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="3D594B594549B64BB41AFEFBFDB81CF0" author="Majewski, E." box="[328,517,366,392]" pageId="10" pageNumber="469" refId="ref15495" refString="Majewski, E. (1882) Systematyczny wykaz owadow Zylkoskrzydlych polskich u nas dotad znalezionych. Insecta Neuroptera Polonica. Ksiegarnia Gebethnera i Wolffa, Warszawa, 42 pp." type="book" year="1882">Majewski (1882</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="3D594B594549B64BB746FEFBFDF01CF1" author="Majewski, E." box="[532,589,366,393]" pageId="10" pageNumber="469" pagination="1 - 39" refId="ref15526" refString="Majewski, E. (1885) Owady Zylkoskrzydle (Neuroptera Polonica). Systematyczny wykaz krajowych sieciarek i prasiatnic. Materyaly do fauny krajowej. Nakladem ksiegarni Teodora Paprockiego i S-ki, Warszawa, 1 - 2, 1 - 39." type="journal article" year="1885">1885</bibRefCitation>
) indicated a questionable record of “ 
<taxonomicName id="9EC84D2B4549B64BB153FEFAFB7A1CF0" box="[1025,1223,366,392]" class="Insecta" family="Panorpidae" genus="Panorpa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mecoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="469" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fasciata">
<emphasis id="6BBCEABA4549B64BB153FEFAFB7A1CF0" box="[1025,1223,366,392]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="469">Panorpa fasciata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
F. (?)” previously published by 
<bibRefCitation id="3D594B594549B64BB47EFE07FE031CD5" author="Belke, G." box="[300,446,402,429]" pageId="10" pageNumber="469" pagination="1 - 114" refId="ref13037" refString="Belke, G. (1859) Rys historyi naturalnej Kamienca podolskiego [Esquisse l'histoire naturelle de Kamienietz Podolski]. Drukarnia Gazety Codziennej, Warszawa, 1859, 1 - 114." type="journal article" year="1859">Belke (1859)</bibRefCitation>
together with other representatives of the genus 
<taxonomicName id="9EC84D2B4549B64BB68AFE06FB871CD4" box="[984,1082,403,428]" class="Insecta" family="Panorpidae" genus="Panorpa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mecoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="469" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="6BBCEABA4549B64BB68AFE06FB871CD4" box="[984,1082,403,428]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="469">Panorpa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="3D594B594549B64BB115FE07FAF91CD4" author="Dziedzielewicz, J." box="[1095,1348,402,428]" pageId="10" pageNumber="469" pagination="26 - 151" refId="ref13821" refString="Dziedzielewicz, J. (1891) Przeglad fauny krajowej owadow siatkoskrzydlych (Neuroptera, Pseudoneuroptera). Sprawozdania Komisji Fizjograficznej Akademii Umiejetnosci w Krakowie, 26, 26 - 151." type="journal article" year="1891">Dziędzielewicz (1891)</bibRefCitation>
also reported “ 
<emphasis id="6BBCEABA4549B64BB5A0FE22FEA61CA9" box="[242,283,439,465]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="469">P.?</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="9EC84D2B4549B64BB473FE23FE091CA8" authority="Fab." authorityName="Fab." box="[289,436,438,464]" class="Insecta" family="Panorpidae" genus="Panorpa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mecoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="469" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fasciata">
<emphasis id="6BBCEABA4549B64BB473FE23FEC71CA8" box="[289,378,438,464]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="469">fasciata</emphasis>
Fab.
</taxonomicName>
” as a questionable species based on G. Belke’s information, and suggested that the record belongs to 
<taxonomicName id="9EC84D2B4549B64BB45DFE4EFE391C8C" authorityName="Rambur" authorityYear="1842" box="[271,388,475,500]" class="Insecta" family="Panorpidae" genus="Panorpa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mecoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="469" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cognata">
<emphasis id="6BBCEABA4549B64BB45DFE4EFE391C8C" box="[271,388,475,500]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="469">P. cognata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. At present, the name 
<taxonomicName id="9EC84D2B4549B64BB72AFE4EFD511C8C" box="[632,748,474,500]" class="Insecta" family="Panorpidae" genus="Panorpa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mecoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="469" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fasciata">
<emphasis id="6BBCEABA4549B64BB72AFE4EFD511C8C" box="[632,748,474,500]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="469">P. fasciata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="9EC84D2B4549B64BB6F7FE4EFB101C8C" authority="Swederus" authorityName="Swederus" authorityYear="1787" box="[933,1197,474,500]" class="Insecta" family="Panorpidae" genus="Panorpa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mecoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="469" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="americana">
<emphasis id="6BBCEABA4549B64BB6F7FE4EFB8A1C8C" box="[933,1079,475,500]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="469">P. americana</emphasis>
Swederus
</taxonomicName>
, which is restricted to the 
<collectingCountry id="21DF76384549B64BB5EDFE6BFEB11F60" box="[191,268,510,536]" name="United States of America" pageId="10" pageNumber="469">U.S.A.</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="3D594B594549B64BB448FE6BFDBA1F60" author="Penny, N. D. &amp; Byers, G. W." box="[282,519,510,537]" pageId="10" pageNumber="469" pagination="365 - 388" refId="ref16510" refString="Penny, N. D. &amp; Byers, G. W. (1979) A Check-List of the Mecoptera of the World. Acta Amazonica, 9 (2), 365 - 388. https: // doi. org / 10.1590 / 1809 - 43921979092365" type="journal article" year="1979">Penny &amp; Byers 1979</bibRefCitation>
). The specimens from SMNH collection were mentioned in 
<bibRefCitation id="3D594B594549B64BB1F3FE6BFF7D1F44" author="Dziedzielewicz, J." pageId="10" pageNumber="469" pagination="38 - 40" refId="ref14051" refString="Dziedzielewicz, J. (1918) Owady siatkoskrzydlowate ziem Polski (Insecta neuropteroidea Poloniae terrarum). Rozprawy i Wiadomo s ci z Muzeum im. Dzieduszyckich, Lwow, 4 (1 - 4), 38 - 40." type="journal article" year="1918">Dziędzielewicz (1918: 39)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
